  "title": "Xtra Gooey Mediterranean Shrimp Toast",
  "description": "A rich and savory solo dinner dish featuring shrimp, feta cheese, and kalamata olives on toasted bread, held together with a gooey vegetable shortening sauce.",
  "cuisine": "Mediterranean",
  "diet": [
    "pescatarian"
